Bottom line... great 3 star hotel, safe area, good location.	Secure and safe location, "El" station right around the corner (State & Lake Stop).	It's incredibly clean and safe.	No hotel safe either.	The most important thing for me as a single traveller though was that it was clean, bright and very safe feeling.	I was in town for biz and booked through Amex package to secure a really great rate.	I can't think of a single thing to complain about, other than the lack of an in-room safe, one of my pet peeves.	Clean, comfortable for the price.